msg: Added PrefixMapping[Impl] to record the prefix mappings of a Model.
Models now extend PrefixMapping, so any model can now do a setNsPrefix.
Those prefixes are passed to the Writer before it writes.
collection.rdf almost certainly has a bug in its use. The daml namespace
was wrong but this isn't the complete problem.
RDFWriter's have been forced to have an enquiry method for finding out
